name: Eternal
description: I think everyone has come across this. You set the alarm for a certain time, and before or after that time you set alarms for + 5-15 minutes. And so they ring non-stop and constantly. In the morning you get annoyed by these alarms and go to wash. The day will pass quite hard, and by the evening you will be tired. It is my problem. And I believe that not only mine.
